<item>
            <title>[SOLR-636] admin page schema link fails for example multicore config</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-636</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If I try to view the schema.xml for a single core, using the gui link:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:8983/solr/core1/admin/file/?file=schema.xml&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://localhost:8983/solr/core1/admin/file/?file=schema.xml&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I get instead:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;HTTP ERROR: 404&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;NOT_FOUND&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;RequestURI=/solr/admin/file/&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Powered by Jetty://&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt; linux x86_64 rhel ibm-java-6 prepackaged jetty&lt;br/&gt;
solr snapshot 7-15-2008 &lt;/p&gt;</environment>
